[10/06/2019 05:37:22] <font color="#ffff00">Hola, Nathalie.</font>
[10/06/2019 05:37:22] <font color="#ffffff">Hola, Julie.</font>
[10/06/2019 05:37:23] <font color="#ffff00">Estaba mirando la casa.</font>
