[10/06/2019 15:59:47] <font color="#ffffff">Paso.</font>
[10/06/2019 15:59:47] <font color="#00ff00">Rebote.</font>
[10/06/2019 15:59:49] <font color="#ffffff">Castizo.</font>
[10/06/2019 15:59:49] <font color="#00ff00">No es correcto. Rebote.</font>
